Is it grey and teal or pink and white? Facebook followers of online retailer Asos are divided on the colour of a pair of shoes shared by the store. The picture has gone viral on the platform and has received more than 1,000 likes and 6,000 comments, and has been shared more than 750 times as people seek answers. For some, they have seen both the combination of grey and teal as well as that of pink and white. Take our poll and let us know which colour combination you see.